{"tid":2357874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英央行同意脫歐導致英國經濟損失4%的估算","createTime":"2021-01-07T17:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T07:10:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5c464ace9b5237d5414e596b265f415e40f146","tid":2357874,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/英央行同意脫歐導致英國經濟損失4-的估算-020928612.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E8%84%AB%E6%AD%90%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%B4%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B14-%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97-020928612.html&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=b5994669\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/英央行同意脫歐導致英國經濟損失4-的估算-020928612.html</a><br />\n<br />\n英倫銀行行長貝利表示，英國與歐盟去年底取得的貿易協議大致符合該行預期，當時央行預計英國脫歐導致英國經濟在未來3年損失共2%。但脫歐成本會隨時間增加，影響將非常長遠，基於經濟實際上如何調節，英國經濟長遠將因脫歐損失3%至4%為大致正確的估算。然而實際影響視乎英國未來數周遇到的問題，與及英國經濟有多快速地適應新貿易安排。 英國預算責任辦公室早前估算英國脫歐導致英國經濟損失最多4%。"},{"pid":"aee0c13fea38d1795020f79a97f4423c0d992421","tid":2357874,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}